<P>
EAST L.A. YMCA RECEIVES HONOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Volunteers and staff members from the Weingart-East Los Angeles YMCA received 
an award for program development and implementation at the 107th annual meeting 
of the YMCA of Metropolitan Los Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
The East Los Angeles Y offers a variety of courses, including citizenship and 
English as a second language. An ESL/amnesty course is given in 10-week 
sessions. The next session starts in mid-October. Information: (213) 260-7005 
</P>
</TEXT>
