<P>
A. C. Martin Wins Shuwa Job: Shuwa Investments Corp. selected A. C. Martin 
&amp; Associates as the master planner for its proposed development for a 
7-acre downtown property located between Eighth, Ninth, Hope and Flower 
streets. A. C. Martin, one of the largest Los Angeles architectural and 
