desert near Needles in Southern California. ; Photo, A helicopter and its crew 
searches the rugged Arizona desert for a Marine observation plane and its two 
crew members. ; Photo, Marine Cpl. Paul J. Romano walks back to his helicopter 
after refueling at the Lake Havasu airport. He and others are scouring a 
500-square-mile area for the two missing Marines fliers. DON KELSEN / Los 
