<HEADLINE>
<P>
PLAN ALLOWS 3 NEW CARRIERS IN 1990 AT WAYNE AIRPORT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN O'DELL, Times Staff Writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Table, DAILY FLIGHTS AT JOHN WAYNE AIRPORT ; Photo, 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
JOHN WAYNE AIRPORT; TRANSPORTATION ROUTES; AIRLINES -- ORANGE COUNTY; AIRPORTS 
-- ORANGE COUNTY; SOUTHWEST AIRLINES CO; MIDWEST AIRLINES INC; BRANIFF INC; 
AIRPORT NOISE; TRAVEL RESTRICTIONS; FEDERAL EXPRESS CORP; UNITED PARCEL SERVICE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
