Photo, Super Saver Cinemas 7 lobby, above, has flashing lights and neon tubes 
that pulse to a musical beat. Below, moviegoers queue up outside the complex, 
which opened last Friday in Seal Beach. DON KELSEN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
